{"tid":624684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食鼻屎有益健康！ MIT及哈佛專家發現鼻屎能防蛀牙增強免疫力","createTime":"2018-04-11T00:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T03:49:20.000Z","uid":160807,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28e4123d02f7e546a8578f711eb85d9ddcbbaa96","tid":624684,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:44:18.000Z","msg":"部分小孩習慣會在挖鼻後，把挖出的「鼻屎」放到口中──等等！先別作嘔，專家稱為人家長或師長者不應阻止，因這個行為也有醫學根據。研究發現鼻屎不但可令牙齒健康，甚至可增強免疫力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/564266/org/1531e7b0fe1141e5178c954a6f8cde8a.jpg/TW-nnyg976GP8qCnABh2Iv1tUU5lZgxMRG9FZERvRWQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F564266%2Forg%2F1531e7b0fe1141e5178c954a6f8cde8a.jpg%2FTW-nnyg976GP8qCnABh2Iv1tUU5lZgxMRG9FZERvRWQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1fde9346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「鼻屎」是由鼻黏膜分泌的鼻水，混合空氣的塵埃或微生物等變乾而成。挖鼻後把鼻屎隨處「飛彈」固然是不衛生行為，家長都會千方百計阻止小孩手多多，或把自己挖出的鼻屎放到口中。<br />\n<br />\n鼻水能防止蛀牙　吞下能增強免疫力<br />\n<br />\n不過，近日有專家發現這個吃「鼻屎」的行為很可能是來自祖先的本能行為，而且有益無害。一群來自麻省理工學院（Massachusetts Institute of Technology，MIT）與哈佛大學（Harvard University）的研究學者，在最一期《美國微生物學會期刊》（American Society for Microbiology Journal）中發表文章，指出「吃鼻屎有益健康」。<br />\n<br />\n研究發現「鼻屎」能預防呼吸道感染，對抗愛滋病病毒，鼻屎附帶的鼻水亦可阻止細菌黏附在牙齒上造成蛀牙，而吞下鼻水甚至有預防胃潰瘍的功效。有研究正嘗試分離「鼻屎」中的有益成份，製成牙膏或香口膠，用作防止蛀牙。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員亦指出，由於鼻屎本身因混有細菌，當進入消化道就能啟動免疫系統發揮作用，增進腸道健康。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/89273/%E9%A3%9F%E9%BC%BB%E5%B1%8E%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%8A%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7-mit%E5%8F%8A%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%BC%BB%E5%B1%8E%E8%83%BD%E9%98%B2%E8%9B%80%E7%89%99-%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F89273%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25BC%25BB%25E5%25B1%258E%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%259B%258A%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7-mit%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2593%2588%25E4%25BD%259B%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25BC%25BB%25E5%25B1%258E%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%259B%2580%25E7%2589%2599-%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2585%258D%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%258A%259B&d=6xk%2F9XeIPJjZF1upQV6olQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=cfc93f0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/89273/%E9%A3%9F%E9%BC%BB%E5%B1%8E%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%8A%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7-mit%E5%8F%8A%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E9%BC%BB%E5%B1%8E%E8%83%BD%E9%98%B2%E8%9B%80%E7%89%99-%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E5%8A%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人想食小草啲鼻屎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47094cc38fc78d530a82acadfcb90395dc816826","tid":624684,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8de9435029ee14023beda1be84c5d4dd22e538c","tid":624684,"uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:20:54.000Z","msg":"連登冇人食鼻屎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64d5b6c6bb0d7a1a45d6e6e4d0ea467651477fb","tid":624684,"uid":3052,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1AIeAp6gvJRT8FHYGm/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1AIeAp6gvJRT8FHYGm%2Fgiphy.gif&h=0cc5c5e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b8dd395f31d85580ce00490ea196cdd489868cf","tid":624684,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啲細路無人教都識食鼻屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來係本能嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5d198489daae3dca0ddc8e193803f3